text: Zille Huma () is the daughter of the late Melody Queen Madam Noor Jehan and the only one of her four daughters to follow in her mother's footsteps. Today, she is a popular Pakistani pop singer. ==References== Category:Pakistani singers Category:Punjabi people Category:1944 births Category:2014 deaths Category:People from Karachi Category:People from Lahore Category:People of British India
